Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,With high hopes, humans\Nleave Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...to begin a new life in\Nthe space colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.89,0:01:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But the United Earth Sphere\NAlliance gains military power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...and in the name of\NJustice and Peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...seizes control of one\Ncolony after the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The year is After Colony 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation Meteor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,To counter the Alliance's\Ntyranny, rebel colonists...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...bring new arsenals\Nto the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.58,0:01:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...disguising them as\Nshooting stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:02:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Alliance headquarters\Ncatches on to this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:19.96,Wing Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,717.75)\be7\blur6.75}The Gundam Deathscythe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Heero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you ripped up Relena's\Ninvitation yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm her classmate so I'm\Nchoked you'd treat her that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you ashamed of yourself,\Nas a gentleman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.51,0:02:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me sooner next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give it to you instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that Heero?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's him all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he's pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure doesn't look it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's taking you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't deploy the suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The carrier isn't\Nequipped for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop until all underwater\Nmobile suits are deployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, I have Lieutenant Zechs\Nfrom Specials on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What does Treize's little\Npawn want now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having some problems?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,None of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know I may be out{\i0}\N{\i1}of line for saying so.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But don't you think the{\i0}\N{\i1}time spent on this search...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...will affect your evaluation{\i0}\N{\i1}by the Alliance headquarters?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, we're having engine{\i0}\N{\i1}problems with our new submarine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:03:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're wasting the{\i0}\N{\i1}military's money.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like you to let us make\Nsome repairs to our submarine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You mean on MY ship?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And to return the favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...we'll lend you our latest\Nunderwater mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pisces and Cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I read you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll give us a hand if we keep{\i0}\N{\i1}quiet about the engine problems.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're on.{\i0}\N{\i1}Get over here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Zechs, there's\Nnothing wrong with this sub.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only way he'd\Nagree to help us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find\Nwhat we're after.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that everybody's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin our\Nhorsemanship class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we'll practice\Nsome new maneuvers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I'll explain\Nthe main points.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Heero's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I'm sure he's\Naround somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy doesn't need to\Nbe taking any lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep water torpedoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Guiding functions installed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Marina weapons\Nwarehouse; that's not far!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And now for the minor revisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero Yuy, entrance fees unpaid...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Boarding unpaid... cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bursary funds... cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Financial check on\NHeero Yuy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,See you, Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll come over right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter Relena?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd never guess it was\Nyour birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...from that gloomy expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on Relena; show us\Nyour pretty smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so secretive...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He has many secrets;\Nthat's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know his secret;\Nthat's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he said\Nhe's gonna kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Reading some kind of suspense\Nthriller are you, Miss Relena?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Three torpedoes should\Ntrigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...the self-detonation device.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll destroy this thing\Nbefore OZ gets to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Zechs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The detector has picked up\Na trace of metal at point 5500.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Send the Cancer and Pisces.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant, let me handle\Nthis one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't like being in\Nouter space.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pisces will be in the lead and\NCancer will follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be giving orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Zechs, I've got\Nmobile suits from the Marina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like that Captain's\Ncaught on to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,An explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Numerous mobile suits are being\Ndestroyed at this same depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop engines!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the Pisces\Nand Cancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't see the enemy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lost contact with\Nall of our mobile suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch torpedoes to\Nthose coordinates!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But Zechs' submarine\Nis still in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,HE could even be the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The Captain's ship has\Nlaunched torpedoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with all the commotion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:08:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Our enemy's close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't suppose that\NGundam pilot survived?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I doubt it, but be{\i0}\N{\i1}cautious anyway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Try and survive THAT\Nkind of torpedo shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll all die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who sees me has\Ngot a date with his maker!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! How beautiful!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for coming\Nto my birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been so delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to wish you\Na happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really have to\Nleave so soon, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you stay a bit\Nlonger for Relena?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena. I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to apologize Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm old enough to understand\Nhow important your business is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Those pictures...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now for the news.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}According to a military{\i0}\N{\i1}announcement...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the meteorites that entered{\i0}\N{\i1}the atmosphere in five locations...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...disintegrated before{\i0}\N{\i1}reaching the ground.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They weren't manned spacecrafts{\i0}\N{\i1}as previously rumored.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero was in one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what does that make Heero?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he a "Star Prince"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be late for\NRelena's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That looked just like Heero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ is moving ahead\Nwith its plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:56.71,Wing Series Mid-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(852.75,362.25)}Mobile Suit Gundam Wing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna join?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Any experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't tell me\Na bloody thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Beasts only bare their\Nfangs at enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're true to their feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mysterious kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Quatre, I've brought\Nyou some refreshments.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Very, very beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they know how\Nbeautiful Earth is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This should help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should I leave these?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why're you handing a huge\Namount of explosives to a kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's paid in full\Nfor the truck, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Blow them out, Miss Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The candles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't miss the main event.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.43,0:14:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So it looks like Heero's\Nnot here after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe that WAS\NHeero I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see Heero?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, along the coastal road.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But the funny thing is,\Nhe was driving an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Must've been someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,An ambulance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's him all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Which direction was that\Nambulance headed for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,For the military port.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Relena?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please continue the party\Nwithout me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to the port then\Nat least let me give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen such\Na severe expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you going to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found the Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But where's the Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other metal\Nbeing detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's inform Lieutenant Zechs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You've found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah but it's amazing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's not even a scratch!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I must say our enemies have\Nbuilt an impressive beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,However, now that we\Nhave it in our grasp...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...we'll be fierce beasts\Nourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out for the current.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll wait at this depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, get the cables{\i0}\N{\i1}and floats ready.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, what's with the noise?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it self-detonating?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's this light coming from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How can he use a thermal\Nenergy weapon underwater?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I defeated it, Lieutenant Zechs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ's new armor\Nis pretty tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what they were\Nsearching for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on self-detonate mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's identical to mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the location of the\Nself-detonation device.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No sense destroying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use it for parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Load the injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey meds! Move your butts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where'd they go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So it IS you, Heero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Heero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are torpedoes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to me, Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in too deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty obvious that\Nyou're the bad guy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't overdo it; remember,\Nyou're injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you wanna\Nshoot him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I end up\Nthe bad guy here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already risen this high.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Must've miscalculated the tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady, I'm sure you have your\Nreasons for being here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you'd better just leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do yourself a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't had enough?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So it IS my mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, everything is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission, complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows Gundanium's\Nimpact tolerance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.67,0:21:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means he's the\Npilot of the mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Zechs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lost all communication\Nwith the Cancer and Pisces.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They say you won't live\Nonce you see a Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that's not true.
