Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.04,0:23:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero is restrained in the\Nmedical treatment room...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.57,0:23:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the Alliance Military.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.31,0:23:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Duo, in the meantime,\Nplans Heero's escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.05,0:23:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs predicts that a Gundam\Nwill be attacking the Aries...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.05,0:23:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...at the Alliance Military Base\Nof the Mediterranean Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.09,0:23:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's there that Zechs is\Nintroduced to a new weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.76,0:23:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, on Gundam Wing, Episode 3,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:58.77,Wing Next Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\be7\blur6.75\pos(736,715.5)}Five Gundams Confirmed
